The paper focuses on object tracking using convolutional networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning techniques such as Kernelized Correlation Filter (KCF) and convolutional networks also suggests that the paper may fall under sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of hyperspectral videos may also suggest that the paper could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
